review_data.title: Great value for fresh seafood in Zurich
review_data.content: Very nice and fresh seafood with reasonable price. I was there alone, and i had ordered 6 x oyster + 3 choices of seafood tapas + 2 glasses of white wine. The seafood is very fresh and delicious. The bill is very reasonable.

review_data.title: Delicious and such good value for Zurich
review_data.content: We had the seafood tapas and a couple of glasses of excellent chilled dry white wine. The food was delicious, especially the anchovies and the wine was amazing. Best part? The bill! Very reasonable!
